Eriq Timmons, ónyé a maara nke ọma dị ka Freak Nasty, bụ ónyé America na-edekọ hip hop na onye na-emepụta ihe ndekọ si Atlanta. A zụlitere ya na New Orleans. A maara ya nke ọma màkà egwu Top 40 ya "Da' Dip" nke e wepụtara na 1996 nke bụ ihe na-ehi ụra, ma mesịa bụrụ ihe a ma ama n'oge ọkọchị 1997; o mechara ruo n'ọkwa 15 na Hot 100. O mechara wepụta "Do What U Feel" site na abọm Which Way Is Up, mana ọ rughị ihe ịga nke ọma nke abụ gárá aga, na-eme ka ọ bụrụ 87 na chaatị R&B Hot.
Freak Nasty malitere ọrụ ya dị ka DJ na onye na-emepụta hip hop
Ọ bụ otu n'ime mmadụ abụọ, n'otu ìgwè a na-akpọ PMW
Mgbè ahụ ọ chọtara ihe ịga nke ọma na Atlanta, Georgia na abọm mbụ ya Freak Nasty, na-ere  fọrọ nke nta ka ọ bụrụ 300,000

Nke ahụ bụkwa otú o si, bụ ihe kachasị ewu ewu ma ree karịrị nde ise, [ihe odide dị mkpa] karịsịa n'ihi egwu égwu ya "Da' Dip", nké ruru n'ọkwa 15 na Billboard Hot 100. N'afọ 2007, egwú "Do It Just Like a Rockstar" rutere n'ọkwa nke 45 na Billboard Hot 100.
